十萬元以下\r\n罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/110%2c%e4%ba%a4%e8%a8%b4%2c43%2c20211228%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,交訴,43,20211228,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"交訴","JNO":"43","JDATE":"20211228","JTITLE":"過失致死"}